FrageText.de: Sie betätigen den Startschalter, der Startermotor reagiert jedoch nicht. Was kann die mögliche Ursache dafür sein?
FrageText.en: You are pushing the starter switch but the starter motor does not react What are the possible causes?
FrageText.hr: Pritiskate prekidač za start motora, ali motor startera ne reagira. Što može biti mogući uzrok tome?
FrageText.sl: Pritisnete na startno stikalo, vendar se motor ne vžge. Kaj vse so lahko vzroki?
FrageText.tr: Start şalterine basıyorsunuz ancak starter motoru tepki vermiyor. Bunun muhtemel nedeni ne olabilir?

en.Text: The ignition is not turned on
The sidestand is not pulled in
Fuel tap is not turn on
